description_text: Non-slip function. Our toilet has non-slip elements on the base to ensure higher safety when training your child.Splash guard. The children's toilet is equipped with a high splash guard to minimise accidental urine spills.Removable bowl and lid included. The tray is removable for easy emptying and always keep clean. For hygienic reasons, a lid is included that keeps the toilet clean and discreet when your baby is not using it.MAGIC STICKERS Delight your child with our magical side. When it pees, the colour of the sticker changes and shows our smiling sheep!A HUGE PIECE OF OUR EXPERIENCE FOR YOU AT HAND. As parents, we know exactly how much work it is to teach a child to use the toilet. For this reason, we offer you a little guide with our best tips on how to give up nappies.
